snippet.title: Clueless Fashion DS | Full Game Playthrough | No Commentary
snippet.description:
The full playthrough of Glyphic Entertainment's cancelled title, Clueless Fashion for the Nintendo DS. Ran on the DeSmuMe emulator. The full ROM will be available on archive.org tomorrow!

Watch the original documentary 'The Girl Games of Lost Media' here:
https://youtu.be/D8ZUR2De15s
